			<item>
				<title>About Juri</title>
				<link>http://localhost:1313/docs/street-fighter-6/juri/about/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid>http://localhost:1313/docs/street-fighter-6/juri/about/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;Juri is the drive rush character of Street Fighter 6 where all it takes is a drive rush or 2MK DRC to snowball her way to victory. She&amp;rsquo;s a very versatile all-rounder similar to Chun but with a stronger focus on aggression. Her gimmick is &amp;ldquo;Fuha stocks&amp;rdquo; that enhance all of her 236K specials so there&amp;rsquo;s slight resource management, and her 214214P super is an install that enhances her frame data and juggle potential.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
